Remember also https://github.com/symfony/symfony/issues/6045#issuecomment-23319231
In the PR https://github.com/symfony/symfony/pull/5943 the reverse transform in NumberToLocalizedStringTransformer became broken for those without the 'intl' php-extension installed. That is because StubNumberFormatter::parse() do not handle <code>$position != null</code>

